  "title": "Gingerbread Cheesecake Cookies",
  "subtitle": "A cake worth the weighing.",
  "excerpt": "Gingerbread Cheesecake Cookies. A baking recipe from Rebecca's collection, straightforward, reliable, worth weighing rather than scooping.",
  "type": "RECIPE",
  "sourceNotes": "From Rebecca's personal cookbook. Bread recipes draw on the long tradition of home baking, Elizabeth David's English Bread and Yeast Cookery is one of the canonical references in English.",
  "body": {
