    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Gingerbread Cheesecake Cookies. An American family-table recipe, generous, comforting, built for a crowd. Adjustable for what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Cake batters reward weighing over scooping. Room-temperature butter and eggs, raised properly, tested with a skewer.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
